cc:Work.dc:description:
Ramp for accessibility purposes x is the width of the ramp, generally the width of the step the ramp is built for y is the length of the ramp, will influence the steepness of the ramp h is the height of the ramp.
Created with Boxes.py (https://boxes.hackerspace-bamberg.de/) Command line: boxes Ramp Command line short: boxes Ramp
